channel.title: Looking for someone who can make webclients
channel.description:
Hello people. I am looking for someone who really know what they are doing in converting regular client to webclient. Many people failed to do so including me. I am willing to "donate"(Since I can't buy things here I will call it donate) 5 dollars to who ever make the webclient working.
Post, private message me here or email me at administrator@ritzscape.net if you are interested.
P.S For prof that I pay, ask the dude Stupit. I hate him now because I gave him 5 bucks in paypal and he won't even give me the finished webclient... If this is still illegal, I am sorry I did not know.
